                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7719" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0520</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2153 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">另辟“锡”径：百年云锡HRBP“变形记”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Another &quot;tin&quot; path：the HRBP’s &quot;Metamorphosis&quot; in Century-old YunNan Tin Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄波，陈兰兰（通讯作者），王延玲，俞鑫，魏鑫，赵佳豪，刘洋君，谭茹方</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南锡业集团（控股）有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">传统人事事务管理；HRBP；人力资源三支柱；人力资源战略变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Traditional personnel affairs management; HRBP ; Three pillars of human resource; Human resource strategy reform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经历了140年的发展，作为传统国有企业的代表之一，云南锡业集团（控股）有限责任公司（以下简称”云锡”）已成为了世界锡行业的领头羊企业。为了响应市场化变革需求，近年来云锡开启了战略性人力资源管理的转型之路。本案例详述了早期云锡传统人事事务型管理存在的问题和弊端，以及云锡进行人力资源“三支柱”变革的动因，并系统描述了云锡人力资源业务合作伙伴HRBP（Human Resource Business Partner，以下简称HRBP）转型方案的设计、人员的选配到项目试点运行的变革历程。此外，案例中描写了两种不同来源的HRBP在刚到基层业务单位时遇到的不同难题，并展现了这些HRBP在总部专家中心COE（Center of Expertise，以下简称COE）团队的指导下，充分结合发现的业务痛点，定制化地为业务单位制定解决方案的过程，强调了HRBP在企业中的作用和价值。案例期望读者能基于人力资源“三支柱”模式的相关知识，特别是HRBP的活动价值和角色等相关内容，对案例提出的问题进行辩证性地分析、思考和解答。案例为实践中企业如何进行HRBP转型提供了全面而真实的分析场景，尤其是为传统国有企业进行现代化人力资源“三支柱”转型提供了参考和借鉴价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">After 140 years of development, as one of most typical traditional state-owned enterprises, YunNan Tin Group has become the bellwether of the enterprises in the world tin industry. In response to the needs of market change, YunNan Tin Group has embarked on the transformation of strategic human resource management in recent years. This case describes the disadvantages of traditional personnel affairs management in the company and the motivations of the human resource &quot;three pillars&quot; innovation, then introduces the transformation process from the design of HRBP (Human Resource Business Partner) transformation scheme, to personnel selection and the pilot operation of the project. The case then emphatically describes the different problems encountered by HRBP from two different sources when they just arrived at the grass-roots business unit, and illustrates how these HRBP fully customized solutions for business units combining the core problem of the associated business under the guidance of the COE (Center of Expertise) team of the headquarters, which further highlights the role and value of HRBP. It is expected that readers can dialectically analyze, consider and answer the questions raised by the case based on the relevant knowledge of the &quot;three pillars&quot; of human resource, especially some key concepts such as the activity value and role of HRBP. This case provides a comprehensive and real analysis scenario for enterprises to carry out HRBP transformation in practice, and especially provides reference for traditional state-owned enterprises to carry out modern transformation of &quot;three pillars&quot; of human resource.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《战略性人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革的动因；人力资源管理演进阶段；传统人事管理与现代人力资源管理的区别和联系；人力资源“三支柱”模式；人力资源管理者的活动价值、角色和素质（KSAOs）；HRBP工作运行中的可能障碍；人力资源“三支柱”适用时机和条件。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
